<h3 id="estratÃ©gia-01---union-de-todos-coletados">EstratÃ©gia 01 - Union de todos coletados</h3>

<h4 id="union-de-todos-os-textos-coletados">Union de todos os textos coletados</h4>

<p>A primeira <strong>estratÃ©gia</strong> serÃ¡ fazer o <strong>resumo</strong> apÃ³s a uniÃ£o de todos os textos coletados na pesquisa</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">textos_final2</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">' '</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">join</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="n">p2</span> <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">p</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">textos</span> <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">p2</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">p</span><span class="p">])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">parser</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">PlaintextParser</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">from_string</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">textos_final2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">Tokenizer</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'portuguese'</span><span class="p">))</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">lhm_sumarizador</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">LuhnSummarizer</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">stm</span><span class="p">)</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">lhm_sumarizador</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">stop_words</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">stops</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">resumo</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">lhm_sumarizador</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">parser</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">document</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">sentences_count</span><span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">parser</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">document</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">sentences</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<h4 id="resumos---unions">Resumos - Unions</h4>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">i</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">r</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">enumerate</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">resumo</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">"SentenÃ§a:"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">i</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">r</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="k">print</span><span class="p">()</span>
    <span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">"**********************************"</span><span class="p">)</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

